@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### ─── AUTH ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 1. Register a new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Login — REST Client auto-extracts the token for all requests below
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### ⬇ Run step 2 first — this variable is used by every protected request
@token = {{login.response.body.$.token}}

### ─── MOVIES ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 3. Browse popular movies (public — no token needed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/movies

### 4. Search movies (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/movies?query=inception

### 5. Get movie details — also pushes to recently-viewed stack
###    tmdbId 27205 = Inception
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/movies/27205
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Get recently viewed stack (should show Inception after step 5)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/movies/recently-viewed
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── RATINGS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 7. Rate Inception (score 1–10)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ratings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "tmdbId": 27205,
  "score": 9
}

### 8. Rate another movie to improve recommendation quality (The Dark Knight = 155)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ratings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "tmdbId": 155,
  "score": 10
}

### 9. View your ratings — need userId from the login response
# @name loginForId
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{"email": "test@example.com", "password": "password123"}

###
@userId = {{loginForId.response.body.$.userId}}
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}/ratings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── WATCHLIST ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 10. Add Inception to watchlist
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/watchlist
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "tmdbId": 27205
}

### 11. View watchlist
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/watchlist
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Remove Inception from watchlist
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/watchlist/27205
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── RECOMMENDATIONS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 13. Get personalized recommendations
###     Rate a few movies first (steps 7-8) for collaborative filtering results.
###     Falls back to popular movies for new users with no ratings.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recommendations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── SECURITY CHECK ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 14. Unauthenticated request — should return 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ratings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tmdbId": 27205,
  "score": 8
}
